                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160110-83-off472 t18160110-83-cd473"></join>, one pair of shoes, value 8s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18160110-83-victim773" type="victimName">
